OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779289870
OL,3,CThree sisters who drowned in sea off
OL,4,CBrighton named as father pays tribute
OL,6,FThree women who drowned in the sea off
OL,7,FBrighton were sisters, Sussex Police
OL,8,Fhas confirmed.
OL,10,FJane Adetoro, 36, Christina Walter,
OL,11,F32, and 31-year-old Rebecca Walter
OL,12,Ffrom the Uxbridge area of London
OL,13,Fdrowned in the water in the early
OL,14,Fhours of Wednesday 13 May.
OL,16,FIn an emotional tribute, their father
OL,17,FJoseph said: "Today, with a heart full
OL,18,Fof sorrow and love, I pay tribute to
OL,19,Fmy beloved daughters ` Jane,
OL,20,FChristina, and Becky ` whose lives
OL,21,Fended so tragically far too soon.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779289870
OL,3,CThree sisters who drowned in sea off
OL,4,CBrighton named as father pays tribute
OL,6,F"No words can truly describe the pain
OL,7,Fof losing three daughters in the prime
OL,8,Fof their lives. Jane, Christina, and
OL,9,FBecky were more than daughters to me;
OL,10,Fthey were my joy, my strength, and the
OL,11,Fbeautiful light that filled our family
OL,12,Fwith happiness and love.
OL,14,F"Each of you was unique and precious
OL,15,Fin your own special way. Your smiles
OL,16,Fbrightened dark days, your laughter
OL,17,Fbrought comfort, and your presence
OL,18,Fmade life more meaningful. Though your
OL,19,Ftime on earth was short, the impact
OL,20,Fyou made will remain in our hearts
OL,21,Fforever.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779289870
OL,3,CThree sisters who drowned in sea off
OL,4,CBrighton named as father pays tribute
OL,6,F"Jane, your strength and loving spirit
OL,7,Fwill never be forgotten. Christina,
OL,8,Fyour kindness and beautiful heart
OL,9,Ftouched so many lives. Becky, your
OL,10,Fwarmth and joyful soul brought
OL,11,Fhappiness wherever you went. You were
OL,12,Fdeeply loved, and you will always be
OL,13,Fdeeply missed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779289870
OL,3,CThree sisters who drowned in sea off
OL,4,CBrighton named as father pays tribute
OL,6,F"The tragedy of losing all three of
OL,7,Fyou has left an emptiness that words
OL,8,Fcannot heal. There are days when the
OL,9,Fgrief feels unbearable, yet I hold
OL,10,Ftightly to the memories we shared `
OL,11,Fthe laughter, the conversations, the
OL,12,Flove, and the bond that death can
OL,13,Fnever take away.
OL,15,F"Though you are no longer here beside
OL,16,Fus, your spirits live on in our hearts
OL,17,Fevery day. Love like yours never dies.
OL,18,FYou will forever remain a part of our
OL,19,Flives, our prayers, and our memories.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779289870
OL,3,CThree sisters who drowned in sea off
OL,4,CBrighton named as father pays tribute
OL,6,F"Rest peacefully, my precious
OL,7,Fdaughters ` Jane, Christina, and
OL,8,FBecky. You may be gone from our sight,
OL,9,Fbut never from our hearts.
OL,11,F"Forever loved. Forever missed.
OL,12,FForever remembered."
OL,14,FEmergency services responded to an
OL,15,Fincident reported at Brighton beach
OL,16,Fjust before 6am on Wednesday 13 May.
OL,18,FThe bodies of the three women were
OL,19,Fpulled from the water near Black Rocks
OL,20,Fcar park in Madeira Drive on the
OL,21,Fseafront.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
