OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779289870
OL,3,CThree sisters who drowned in sea off
OL,4,CBrighton named as father pays tribute
OL,6,FAn HM Coastguard helicopter, Sussex
OL,7,FPolice, RNLI lifeboats and South East
OL,8,FCoast Ambulance Service all attended
OL,9,Fthe scene.
OL,11,FThe beach reopened just after 7pm on
OL,12,FWednesday evening, having been closed
OL,13,Fall day so enquiries and searches
OL,14,Fcould be carried out.
OL,16,FLocal political figures including
OL,17,FCouncillor Bella Sankey, Chris Ward MP
OL,18,Fand Sian Berry MP were among those who
OL,19,Fpaid tribute to the women.
OL,26,@zD@Gsp
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
