OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779289870
OL,3,CThree sisters who drowned in sea off
OL,4,CBrighton named as father pays tribute
OL,6,FOn Thursday 14 May, officers confirmed
OL,7,Fthe women had been identified and
OL,8,Ftheir next of kin has been informed,
OL,9,Fbut that formal identification
OL,10,Fprocedures are now being undertaken.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday (20 May) Chief
OL,13,FSuperintendent Adam Hays, Divisional
OL,14,FCommander for Brighton and Hove said:
OL,15,F"The thoughts of everyone at Sussex
OL,16,FPolice are with the family of Jane,
OL,17,FChristina and Rebecca following this
OL,18,Fdevastating loss.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
