OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779289870
OL,3,CThree sisters who drowned in sea off
OL,4,CBrighton named as father pays tribute
OL,6,F"I know this incident has had a
OL,7,Fprofound impact on the local community
OL,8,Fin Brighton, and across the country
OL,9,Fand I'd like to reassure the public we
OL,10,Fwill leave no stone unturned in our
OL,11,Finvestigation to understand exactly
OL,12,Fwhat led to the tragic events of that
OL,13,FWednesday morning.
OL,15,F"This investigation will continue in
OL,16,Fearnest, with Jane, Christina and
OL,17,FRebecca's family at its centre. I
OL,18,Fwould ask that they are given the
OL,19,Fprivacy to come to terms with this
OL,20,Fterrible tragedy."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
